reviews.limitations:
(i) Exact equivariance is guaranteed only for discrete grid symmetries, while continuous-rotation behavior is empirical; 
(ii) Spectral isotropy may reduce expressivity in anisotropic PDE regimes; 
(iii) It is recommended to add a "requirements.txt" file to include all the necessary environment packages;
(iv) Results may depend on grid resolution and geometry complexity; 
(v) The font size of the table is too small.
